My dad mentioned an interesting project to me the other day, posing the challenge of coming up with an interface for examining deep rubrics for grading classes, or businesses, or anything that needs a grade. The idea is that you have a tree of different aspects that go into an overall grade. The interface needs to show this tree breakdown, while showing several controls with each item in the list. In short, the interface needs a <a title="Tree Table" href="http://designinginterfaces.com/firstedition/index.php?page=Tree-Table">Tree Table</a>.
